{bold}Monthly Letter{nobold}
{p} {p}
{bold}Pixel64 ZIII{nobold}{p}
    Here are some extra information about this new card:
{p} {p}
    Graphics card for the Amiga 3000 and Amiga 4000,{p}
    Based on the GD5434,{p}
    4Mb of graphics ram,{p}
    Flash rom for in situ upgrade (Upgrade possible within the Amiga!){p}
    Include a full brigde to a real PCI V2.2 bus!{p}
    3 PCI connectors (5V and 3.3V compliants){p}
    Support of the PCI autoconfiguration sequence (plug and play){p}
    Support any PCI 3D accelerators,{p}
    Support any 100Mb PCI Ethernet board,{p}
    Support any PCI Sound card,
{p} {p}
    Target price: 1500 to 1900Frs (USD200 to USD260)
{p} {p}
    Available: Soon!
{p} {p}
